This is a Tab Organiser. It uses chrome's built in group tab manager. It is a free to use extension for google chrome.

By Lucas H

How to setup:

1. Go to chrome extension by searching up chrome://extensions or clicking the menu bar then selecting the extensions button (has a puzzle piece icon).

2. In there, look at the top right corner and turn on dev mode.

3. Then 3 options will pop up. Click load uppacked.

4. Click the folder named "TabOrganizer" and select it. 

Then you are done! 

Enjoy the extension.
